## Project Structure

```text
app/              ← unified Python service (FastAPI + SQLAlchemy + opensearch-py + AI/ML)
app/migrations/   ← SQL applied by app/scripts/migrate.py
app/scripts/      ← migrate.py, snapshotdb.py, reindex_products.py, search_relevance_check.py
opensearch/       ← index mapping JSON + init.sh
```

## Commands

```bash
# Install deps (uv)
make install

# Run app locally
make dev

# DB / search
make migratedb
make snapshotdb
make opensearchinit
make reindexproducts
```

## Code Style

Python 3.11: follow PEP 8, use `ruff` for lint/format, `snake_case` for files and functions, `PascalCase` for classes and SQLAlchemy models, `PascalCase` + suffix for Pydantic schemas (e.g. `ProductResponse`).

